'''硫酸铒'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为Er<sub>2</sub>(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>，存在无水物、四水合物和八水合物。<ref>Bukovec, Natasa; Bukovec, Pteter; Siftar, Joze. Salts and double salts of rare earths.  I.  Thermal analysis of hydrated sulfates. ''Vestnik Slovenskega Kemijskega Drustva'', 1975. 22 (1-4): 5-17. ISSN: 0560-3110.</ref><ref>Mathias S. Wickleder. Syntheses, crystal structures, and thermal behavior of Er2(SO4)​3·8H2O and Er2(SO4)​3·4H2O. ''Zeitschrift fuer Anorganische und Allgemeine Chemie'', 1999. 625 (9): 1548-1555. ISSN: 0044-2313.</ref>
==制备==
用[[硫酸|硫酸]]溶解[[氧化铒|氧化铒]]，可以得到硫酸铒。<ref name=zb />
